levelRequirements.name: Beginner
levelRequirements.privilege: Can upload, can vote on requests but is limited to downloading a total of 10GB per 24 hours (includes freeleech).

levelRequirements.name: Perv
levelRequirements.privilege: Can make content requests in Requests area, can access Top 10, can use the notifications system, can bookmark torrents, can create collages and can create a personal collage.

levelRequirements.name: Member
levelRequirements.privilege: Can view site statistics, can create polls in the forums, can add multiple tags at once, can access the invite forums, can set and can use a torrent signature.

levelRequirements.name: Senior Member
levelRequirements.privilege: Can use advanced bbcode tags and can download multiple torrents at once.

levelRequirements.name: Uploader
levelRequirements.privilege: Can view torrent snatchlists, can view torrent peerlists, can delete tags, can make freeleech torrents, can download VIP torrents and can use invites when necessary.
